<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= writerId %>님의 상점 - 4989(사구팔구)</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">

  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark mb-4 shadow-sm">
    <div class="container">
      <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/">🛒 4989(사구팔구)</a>
      <a class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm" href="/">메인 장터로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="p-4 mb-4 bg-white rounded shadow-sm border-start border-primary border-4">
      <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark m-0">🛍️ '<%= writerId %>' 님의 미니 상점</h4>
      <p class="text-muted small mb-0 mt-1">이 판매자가 등록한 총 <span class="text-danger fw-bold"><%= userProducts.length %></span>개의 상품이 진열되어 있습니다.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-3 row-cols-lg-4 g-4">
      <% if (userProducts.length === 0) { %>
        <div class="col-12 text-center my-5">
          <p class="text-muted fs-5">현재 판매 중인 상품이 없습니다.</p>
        </div>
      <% } else { %>
        <% userProducts.forEach(product => { %>
          <div class="col">
            <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm border-1 rounded-3 overflow-hidden bg-white <%= (product.stock || 0) <= 0 ? 'opacity-50' : '' %>">
              <div style="height: 180px; overflow: hidden; background-color: #f8f9fa;">
                <img src="<%= product.image %>" class="w-100 h-100" style="object-fit: cover;" alt="상품 이미지">
              </div>
              
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column p-3">
                <h5 class="card-title fw-bold text-dark text-truncate mb-1" style="font-size: 1.1rem;"><%= product.title %></h5>
                
                <% if ((product.stock || 0) > 0) { %>
                  <p class="card-text text-danger fw-bold mb-2" style="font-size: 1.2rem;">
                    <%= product.price.toLocaleString() %>원
                  </p>
                <% } else { %>
                  <p class="card-text text-danger fw-bold mb-2" style="font-size: 1.2rem;">품절</p>
                <% } %>
                
                <p class="card-text text-muted small text-truncate mb-3" style="max-height: 40px;">
                  <%= product.content %>
                </p>
                
                <div class="mt-auto">
                  <% if ((product.stock || 0) > 0) { %>
                    <a href="/product/<%= product._id %>" class="btn btn-secondary w-100 fw-bold py-2" style="font-size: 0.95rem;">상세보기</a>
                  <% } else { %>
                    <button class="btn btn-secondary w-100 fw-bold py-2" style="font-size: 0.95rem;" disabled>구매 불가</button>
                  <% } %>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% }) %>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer class="text-center py-4 my-5 text-muted border-top small">
    &copy; 2026 4989(사구팔구) 이진혁 이서준 문지송 | All Rights Reserved.
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>